## What to expect when you get in touch

Before our first call, I will review your site, your key competitors, and the search landscape for your sector. That way, we can have a productive conversation from the start. I will share initial observations, outline where the biggest opportunities are, and explain what a realistic engagement would look like.

If SEO is not the right investment for your business right now, I will say so. I would rather be honest upfront than take on work that will not deliver a return.

